Introduction
Application to communicate with firewall via grpc, and do HW offload on Nvidia
BlueField DPU

Prerequisite
GRPC libraries installed at /root/local/

Usage
1. Compile DPDK and daemon, make sure to run the shell properly to have ENV updated
# cd firewall_offload
# . build.sh

2. Setup hugepages
E.g, # ./firewall_offload/usertools/dpdk-setup.sh

3. Make sure to create 1 VF for each PF on x86 side

4. Run app
# cd firewall_offload/daemon

If no grpc address and port is given, localhost will be used 
# ./build/firewall_offload -n 1 -w 0000:03:00.0,representor=[0] -w 0000:03:00.1,representor=[0]

If grpc address and port are given
# ./build/firewall_offload -n 1 -w 0000:03:00.0,representor=[0] -w 0000:03:00.1,representor=[0] -- -a 10.9.150.185 -p 1234
